<p class="indent0" style="-uslm-lc:I11" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">For purposes of this section and section 179B(b), in the calculation of average daily domestic refinery run or retained production, only refineries which on <date date="2003-04-01">April 1, 2003</date>, were refineries of the refiner or a related person (within the meaning of section 613A(d)(3)), shall be taken into account.</p>
